




{"id":4980,"date":"2021-05-31T14:12:33","date_gmt":"2021-05-31T07:12:33","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/?p=4980"},"modified":"2022-06-28T13:22:25","modified_gmt":"2022-06-28T06:22:25","slug":"giai-phap-camera-truc-tuyen-danh-cho-giao-duc","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/giai-phap-camera-truc-tuyen-danh-cho-giao-duc\/","title":{"rendered":"Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p camera tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn d\u00e0nh cho Gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng xa x\u1ec9 v\u00ec gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng l\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1ed1n d\u0129 lu\u00f4n di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb bao n\u0103m nay. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1eeb l\u00fac d\u1ecbch Covid x\u1ea3y ra v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc sinh, sinh vi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 bu\u1ed9c B\u1ed9 Gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i ra ch\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c h\u1ecdc tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o l\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc di\u1ec5n ra theo \u0111\u00fang k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4982 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/He-thong-camera-danh-cho-giao-duc.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"453\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p>Vi\u1ec7c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p, c\u00e1c ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m, \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec3n khai kh\u00e1 r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2020. \u0110\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh cho c\u00f4ng cu\u1ed9c \u1ea5y, h\u00f4m nay Inno Vi\u1ec7t Nam xin gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m Camera tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn \u2013 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p c\u1ef1c k\u00ec h\u1eefu \u00edch gi\u00fap n\u00e2ng cao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4981 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/camera-education.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"492\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 85%;\">Camera tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn INNO<\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Camera theo d\u00f5i t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00f4ng minh chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng, v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c th\u00f4ng tin gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c<\/p>\n<p>H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 xu\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng video v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 1080p \/ 60fps<\/p>\n<p>Zoom quang 20x v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng zoom \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh t\u1eeb xa, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh \u0111\u1ed9 d\u00e0i ti\u00eau c\u1ef1.<\/p>\n<p>Camera c\u00f3 b\u1ed9 x\u1eed l\u00fd t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 cao t\u00edch h\u1ee3p, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c thu\u1eadt to\u00e1n ph\u00e2n t\u00edch theo d\u00f5i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh WDR h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f3a m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00e0 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau.<\/p>\n<p>\u1ed4n \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady v\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t cao. Ngo\u00e0i ra, n\u00f3 r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o tr\u00ec.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng xa x\u1ec9 v\u00ec gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng l\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1ed1n d\u0129 lu\u00f4n di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb bao n\u0103m nay. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1eeb l\u00fac d\u1ecbch Covid x\u1ea3y ra v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc sinh, sinh vi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 bu\u1ed9c&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":9125,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[66],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4980","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin-tuc"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4980","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4980"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4980\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":9126,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4980\/revisions\/9126"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/9125"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4980"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4980"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4980"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}